item.title: About Me
item.description:
I am Jingyi Su, currently a software engineer at Google.

“Careers are a jungle gym, not a ladder.” ― Sheryl Sandberg (book).

Over the past decade, I have honed my skills and grown through diverse technical and leadership roles (linkedin), including as a machine learning engineer/researcher, data scientist, and actuary (FSA). These experiences have shaped my ability to adapt, innovate, and tackle complex challenges. I am eager to continue evolving, contributing, and making a meaningful impact in every opportunity I embrace.
